@node "Bugs" "Bug Reporting"


Bug Reports

Not all programmers are perfect. MegaRXDL has been tested on an A2000 o3o
40mhz and a stock A500 68000 and has not faulted.. I have run it with a few
mem test utils, but not Enforcer© as I do not have a MMU. To my knowledge
there are no known bugs, nor does it do any harm to your system.

I however accept that there may be bugs of which I am not aware. Bugs reports
are therefore welcome (even if you are not a registered user). I cannot
promise to fix all bugs, but I will try my best. If you find any bug or
problem, please indicate whether it can be reproduced (bugs should be
reproduceable).

Post any bugs to me in XENOLINK_UTIL or Netmail me at 3:640/800 

